
                     BENGALI WRITER TeX INTERFACE
                            Version 3.0.1


This is the README file for the package bwti. This package consists of
fonts for the Bengali alphabet written in METAFONT. You can use these
fonts in your TeX or LaTeX documents. A style file for easier access
to symbols is also provided.


